{"tid":294401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無手足試過飲到好醉？","createTime":"2017-06-23T02:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T05:21:38.000Z","uid":11354,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2fbcad0fbd05bb1374e6565f6c58a24f707123bf","tid":294401,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:48:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日女朋友去左日本旅行 <br />\n所以屋企得番自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住尋晚，我沖完涼 <br />\n發覺電話有十幾個misscall <br />\n原來我朋友岩岩比男友飛左 <br />\n喊哂口咁同我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後傾左成個鐘電話 <br />\n佢忽然話：不如出來陪我飲酒？ <br />\n但係個陣已經成十一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我見屋企無咩人 <br />\n又懶出去 <br />\n就話：不如你上來啦 我屋企又齊酒 <br />\n有私人空間又慳錢 <br />\n於是佢就上左來... <br />\n我地vodka,rum,啤酒,blue curacao, tequila <br />\n咩都溝下來飲 <br />\n結果唔使一個鐘兩個已經醉醉地同好high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n突然 <br />\n佢對眼水汪汪咁問我： <br />\n你可唔可以 錫我一淡？ <br />\n可能真係能成為密友大概總帶著愛 <br />\n我竟然諗都無諗就錫左落去 <br />\n結果我地越咀越激 <br />\n互相纏住大家條頸 <br />\n舌頭交纏住咁行左入我房 <br />\n一攤上床 <br />\n我地互相摷左陣大家就埋牙 <br />\n詳細就唔多講 <br />\n只可以講係幾開心 <br />\n大家都出左三次先攬住訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家覺得好對唔住女朋友 <br />\n同埋覺得同佢既友誼變左質 <br />\n巴絲你地話點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e93d93921e07d86d1ad262466b8a9dbbf8c4289","tid":294401,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:55:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89ff5a0cf7cc15b3ec6ccd133810687090a2de60","tid":294401,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我</blockquote><br />\n廢"},{"pid":"d8a715935bf931c9e99efaf34b4fda9449124de5","tid":294401,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:04:42.00